Loma sukuli kɩtɛzʊʊ, pɩkɛ ɛyaa kpeekpe mba pɛwɛna waɖɛ se papɩzɩɣ pala sukuli ŋgʊ, kɩwɛ [[Loma]] tɛtʊ taa [[Togo]] ɛjaɖɛ. Patʊlɩ sukuli ŋgʊ Loma nɛ hayi kiŋ tɛtʊ taa, [[salaŋ fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 14 pɩnaɣ [[1970]]. Peenɛɛ sukuli kɩtɛzʊʊ lɛɛzɩ mbʊ lɛ Peenɛɛ peeɖe sukuli sɔsɔʊ ŋgʊ ɖɩyaɣ se ISB ŋgʊ ŋgʊ kɩɩwɛ ɖooo pɩnaɣ [[1965]]. [[Lakɩŋ fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 9 pɩnaɣ [[2001]], pɛlɛzɩ hɩɖɛ sukuli ŋgʊ nɛ pɩpɩsɩ se Loma sukuli kɩtɛzʊʊ.  
[[Fichier:Grain_de_Sel_Togo,_Inc_in_Lome_at_the_University_of_Lome.jpg|vignette|Grain de Sel Togo, Inc in Lome at the University of Lome]]

Loma sukuli kɩtɛzʊʊ wɛna kɩ-taa ɖɩwɩlɩyɛ pilinzi kagbaanzɩ nɛ sukuli naa loɖo nɛ tɩlɩyaa aŋgba naatozo. Ɖɩnaɣ lɛɣtʊ tɩnaa pɩlʊʊ (FDS), tɔnʊʊ taa alaafɩya piliŋga (FSS), tɔsʊʊ huu nɛ ɛzɩma tɔsʊʊ ɛɖɛna ɛsɩnda yɔ (FASEG), paɣtʊ tɩnaa hɔɔlʊʊ (FDD), takayasɩ mayaa nɛ ɛyʊ yɔɔ tɩlɩtʊ tɔm (FLESH).
[[File:Founder, speaking during Seminar in Togo.jpg|thumb|Founder, speaking during Seminar in Togo]]
Loma sukuli kɩtɛzʊʊ ŋgʊ kɩwɛna ɖooo pɩnaɣ [[2013]] [[kɔlaɣ fenaɣ]] tɛmtʊ alɩwaatʊ taa kɛ pʊtʊ weyi ɖɩyaɣ se Wi-Fi, pʊtʊ ɛnʊ eyekina nɛ ɛyʊ tamsɩ ɛ-tɩ nɛ ɛjaɖɛ kpeekpe yɔɔ mbʊ kenkeŋ lakɩ yɔɔ, ɛntɛrɩnɛtɩ tɔm pɔyɔɔdʊʊ mbʊ yɔ. 

